Package: beaver-mail
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: SW <stefan@welebny.com>
Installed-Size: 7
Depends: neomutt, isync, msmtp, ca-certificates
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Description: Beaver mail stack (neomutt + mbsync + msmtp)
 Installs a Braille-friendly, terminal-only mail stack:
 neomutt for reading, isync/mbsync for IMAP sync, and msmtp for sending.
